        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves conditional logic, dynamic SQL-like behavior with XML path, and exception handling, making it moderately complex. It also includes logging and error handling mechanisms, which add to its complexity."
        }
      ]
    },
